Objects.Text: * I'm talking! Isn't that great? Yapping is seriously my favorite! Like, totes cool and stuff...

LinkedAction.Text: * My dialogue is so freakin' epic.

* Letting me yap? Great! Nothing beats even MORE yapping! Y'know, it's my favorite thing to do and whatnot sooo... Yeah!
Gosh, if I yapped any more, my mouth would fall off! For realsies!
